    "title": "Lead SEO Specialist at Grofers Advisory Limited",
    "description": "Grofers Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a SEO Specialist for our Patna operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Grofers Advisory Limited:\nGrofers Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Product Management\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Grofers Advisory Limited!",
